    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic restoration. The exterior shows its age with several rust spots, fading paint, and noticeable body damage, while the interior is heavily worn and in need of deep cleaning or reupholstering. Mechanically, it currently struggles to stay running and will likely need major repairs to be roadworthy again. This is a project car sold strictly as-is, ideal for someone looking for a parts vehicle or a complete overhaul project.",
