      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54B32 high-revving power plant, featuring individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double VANOS system. The drivetrain utilizes a robust Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. Suspension kinematics remain factory-perfect, providing the linear handling and tactile feedback expected from this chassis. With an 8,000 RPM redline and an impeccable mechanical pedigree, this vehicle offers an uncompromised naturally aspirated driving experience.",
